@startuml
title Codec System Component Diagram

package "Codec Implementations" {
  [Python Codec] as PyCodec
  [C++ Codec] as CppCodec
  [JavaScript Codec] as JsCodec
  [Java Codec] as JavaCodec
  [Go Codec] as GoCodec
}

package "Shared Format" {
  [PolyArt Format] as Format
  [JSON Serialization] as JSON
  [Binary Serialization] as Binary
}

package "Tools" {
  [PolyArt Converter] as Converter
  [PolyArt Viewer] as Viewer
  [PolyArt Editor] as Editor
}

PyCodec --> Format : reads/writes
CppCodec --> Format : reads/writes
JsCodec --> Format : reads/writes
JavaCodec --> Format : reads/writes
GoCodec --> Format : reads/writes

Format --> JSON : uses
Format --> Binary : uses

Converter --> PyCodec : uses
Viewer --> PyCodec : uses
Editor --> PyCodec : uses

note top of PyCodec
  Reference implementation
  Python 3.11+ with numpy
end note

note bottom of Format
  .polyart for images
  .polyvid for video
end note

@enduml
